               <msContents class="#STM">
                  <summary><p>A single-text manuscript bearing the title <title xml:lang="ta">Cittar Piṭakam</title>, "the basket of the Siddha". It appears to be a medical treatise, judging from the intertitles.</p>
<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (December 2021).</p>
<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p>      </summary>
                  
